CONTEXT KleeneStarNonEndoCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT KleeneStarNonEndoCheck
{+ Test that Kleene star fails on non-endomorphic relations.
   This verifies the type checker correctly rejects t*[A*C] when source and target differ. +}

RELATION t[A*C]
RELATION result[A*C]

RULE testKleeneStarFail: result = t*

ENDCONTEXT
